  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262150/extras/240d667634078acdb6466a826cab7928.avif?t=1774900792\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>Government experiments on a young girl triggered a cosmic shock wave that gifted many young girls with mystical powers. She re-emerges into the world and vows to destroy all of mankind in an act of revenge. A brave group of girls who embraced their powers heads to the battlefield to confront her; not just for the sake of the world, but to pursue their own personal motives and dreams.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose from ten girls with unique fighting skills and pair them with a powerful partner to form an unstoppable team.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Navigate the adventures of a Vanguard Princess in the Story Mode or engage in head-to-head battles in the Versus Mode.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/262150/extras/240d667634078acdb6466a826cab7928.avif?t=1774900792\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>Government experiments on a young girl triggered a cosmic shock wave that gifted many young girls with mystical powers. She re-emerges into the world and vows to destroy all of mankind in an act of revenge. A brave group of girls who embraced their powers heads to the battlefield to confront her; not just for the sake of the world, but to pursue their own personal motives and dreams.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose from ten girls with unique fighting skills and pair them with a powerful partner to form an unstoppable team.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Navigate the adventures of a Vanguard Princess in the Story Mode or engage in head-to-head battles in the Versus Mode.</li></ul>",
